def calculate_right_side_serves(P: int) -> int:
    """
    Calculate the number of times Chef served from the right side of the court.

    Parameters:
    P (int): The number of points obtained by Chef.

    Returns:
    int: The number of times Chef served from the right side of the court.
    """
    return P // 2 - 1
